<h2  class="u-bolt-text-transform-none c-bolt-headline--left u-headline-margin-none c-bolt-headline c-bolt-headline--bold c-bolt-headline--xxxlarge" id="p-50495fa9-e186-472c-8ed1-d87d241ac899">Drive collaborative innovation at scale</h2>
      <p>As change accelerates, those who fall behind get left behind. Pega's low-code platform makes it easy for developers, teams, and engineers to reuse and build new apps to quickly adapt to evolving business needs. Plus, it allows you to specialize processes based on product, region, and more.</p>

  

